# Autonocraft Documentation

When adding or significantly changing a subsystem, update:
- `AGENTS.md` — test list, codebase map, HTTP API if applicable
- `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md` — subsystem design section
- `docs/CODEMAP.md` — file index and task playbook

Do not edit the plan file in `.cursor/plans/`.
